<p>
    <h2>At Gameworld, we take your privacy seriously. </h2>
   <h5> We understand that you trust us with your personal information and we are committed to protecting it. This policy outlines what information we collect from you when you use our website and how we use it.</h5>
   <p class="little-space"></p>
 <h2>Information We Collect: </h2>

 <h5>When you browse our website or make a purchase, we may collect your name, email address, mailing address, phone number, and payment information. We may also collect non-personal information such as your IP address, browser type, and operating system.
 </h5>
 <p class="little-space"></p>
 <h2>How We Use Your Information: </h2>

 <h5>We use your personal information to process orders, respond to inquiries, and provide customer support. We may also use your information to send you promotional emails about new products or special offers, but you can opt-out of these emails at any time.
      </h5>
      <p class="little-space"></p>
<h5>We do not share your personal information with third parties, except as required by law. We may, however, share your non-personal information with third-party service providers who help us operate our website, process orders, or provide customer support.
</h5>
<p class="little-space"></p>
 <h2>Security: </h2>

 <h5>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, and alteration. We use industry-standard encryption technology to secure your sensitive data during transmission. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
 </h5>
 <p class="little-space"></p>
 <h2>Changes to This Policy: </h2>

 <h5>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, so please check back periodically to stay up-to-date. </h5>


</p>
